Package: lassi
Title: Re-implementation of the core linear algebraic routine of the highly
  adaptive LASSO using the Rcpp framework.
Version: 0.0.2.1
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jeremy", "Coyle", email = "jeremyrcoyle@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Nima", "Hejazi", email = "nh@nimahejazi.org",
    role = c("aut")),
  person("David", "Benkeser", email = "benkeser@emory.edu",
    role = c("cph")),
  person("Mark", "van der Laan", email = "laan@berkeley.edu",
    role = c("cph"))
  )
Description: Routines for constructing sparse matrices and indicator functions,
  as required in the formulation of the highly adaptive LASSO algorithm, using
  C++, through the Rcpp framework, to enhance computational performance.
